content.html: My 7yo ADHD baby: I don’t remember where I put my toothbrush I just had in my hand 3 secs ago. Same kid: You told me 8 Mondays ago at 4:11 pm that we could go to target today. I remembered because I was wearing a blue shirt with 3 buttons and you was eating two grapes.

My 7yo ADHD baby: I don’t remember where I put my toothbrush I just had in my hand 3 secs ago. 

Same kid: You told me 8 Mondays ago at 4:11 pm that we could go to target today. I remembered because I was wearing a blue shirt with 3 buttons and you was eating two grapes.
